// DiagramHistoryDropdown
// Version history dropdown for the diagram editor. Identical pattern to
// DesignHistoryDropdown but fetches diagram versions.

FUNCTION formatTimestamp(ts) -> string
  Today: time only. Yesterday: "Yesterday HH:MM". <7d: "DayName HH:MM".
  Older: "Mon DD, HH:MM".

---

FUNCTION DiagramHistoryDropdown(history, onVersionSelect, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a dropdown list of history entries with formatted timestamps.
  Clicking an entry fetches the diagram version content via getVersionAt, then
  calls onVersionSelect(content) if non-null. Closes dropdown.
  Closes on click outside. Disabled when history is empty.

---

FUNCTION handleItemClick(version) -> void
  Fetches version content. Calls onVersionSelect if content is non-null. Closes.
